data.description: Well Maintained, dbl wide Manufactured home on 5 Hard to find acres! 3 bed, 2 bath! Stainless kitchen appliances which include Refrigerator, dishwasher,smooth top electric range,washer and dryer!Primary bedroom has ensuite with walk in closet, large shower, and dbl sinks. Living and kitchen is semi open floorplan, perfect for entertaining.  Home is original to land and perfected as real property.  Freshly painted decks!  Large 15 x 13 deck overlooks this gorgeous land! Property is fully fenced and cross fenced with small animal wire. Partially treed at back of property.  3 frost free water faucets to water your beloved animals, 2 carports, workshop with walk in and roll up door access. 3 arched entry pole barn with enclosed animal stall and farm equipment storage! Currently producing pecan,apple,pear,red and green nectarines,persimmon,jujube, lum and fig trees! Mahindra 2815 Tractor, hay fork, 4' rotary cuttter, belly mower and John Deere d140 riding mower can be purchased separately.
